{"tid":784174,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"一人n個 唔講唔記得踢過呢啲球隊既球員例子","createTime":"2018-08-18T07:06:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-18T15:28:45.000Z","uid":75028,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"4ac89cb7c4a4274046204380659936036192c59f","tid":784174,"uid":75028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T07:06:40.000Z","msg":"林伯特踢過史雲斯<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.pinimg.com/474x/23/c5/fd/23c5fde16f4ad8139611a2bd8c522c77--chelsea-football-swansea.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.pinimg.com%2F474x%2F23%2Fc5%2Ffd%2F23c5fde16f4ad8139611a2bd8c522c77--chelsea-football-swansea.jpg&h=486e0d0b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n里奧費迪南踢過般尼矛夫<br />\n<img src=\"https://hoare89.files.wordpress.com/2010/03/riobournemouth_468x54612.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhoare89.files.wordpress.com%2F2010%2F03%2Friobournemouth_468x54612.jpg&h=14435c91&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n泰利踢過諾定咸森林<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/pix/2014/05/13/article-2627116-1DCDB95D00000578-510_306x423.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fpix%2F2014%2F05%2F13%2Farticle-2627116-1DCDB95D00000578-510_306x423.jpg&h=a3aae950&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n紐卡素傳奇門將基雲踢過哂死敵新特蘭 米堡<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.sporting-heroes.net/content/thumbnails/00149/14800-zoom.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.sporting-heroes.net%2Fcontent%2Fthumbnails%2F00149%2F14800-zoom.jpg&h=5eadf499&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i2-prod.chroniclelive.co.uk/incoming/article6688109.ece/ALTERNATES/s615/JS31750736.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi2-prod.chroniclelive.co.uk%2Fincoming%2Farticle6688109.ece%2FALTERNATES%2Fs615%2FJS31750736.jpg&h=319ca948&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n另一個踢咗紐記廿年既夏柏都踢過新特蘭<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/pix/2016/01/22/19/307993C200000578-0-image-a-8_1453489588505.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fpix%2F2016%2F01%2F22%2F19%2F307993C200000578-0-image-a-8_1453489588505.jpg&h=b9726c57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n查比亞係鏝出身<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/pix/2014/12/27/0B7D7608000005DC-0-image-a-14_1419716944934.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fpix%2F2014%2F12%2F27%2F0B7D7608000005DC-0-image-a-14_1419716944934.jpg&h=23d9c501&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n卡利奧斯都踢過鏝<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.thesun.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/sport-preview-karius-city.jpg?strip=all&amp;quality=100&amp;w=620&amp;h=413&amp;crop=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thesun.co.uk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F04%2Fsport-preview-karius-city.jpg%3Fstrip%3Dall%26quality%3D100%26w%3D620%26h%3D413%26crop%3D1&h=5e206ac1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"90e180b63015586bc9a521fb3ee2e6794ca88a50","tid":784174,"uid":31186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T07:27:40.000Z","msg":"羅比堅尼"},{"pid":"4fa5ce3843338c3669a07adb5249bbd5f884773c","tid":784174,"uid":99700,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T08:04:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i2-prod.liverpoolecho.co.uk/incoming/article7677232.ece/ALTERNATES/s1227b/PA-371068.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi2-prod.liverpoolecho.co.uk%2Fincoming%2Farticle7677232.ece%2FALTERNATES%2Fs1227b%2FPA-371068.jpg&h=1447d1c3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"55c21dcbe7aa72d286d64ab2468e031e7560e0e0","tid":784174,"uid":88862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T08:08:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"91c033a0e1d5162e5370897971872f29718697df","tid":784174,"uid":75028,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T09:51:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.pinkun.com/polopoly_fs/1.1745064.1355820647!/image/697647141